import React from 'react';
import { Button, TextField } from '@material-ui/core';


function DadosUsuario() {
    
    return (
        
        <form>
            <TextField
                id="email"
                label="Email"
                type="email"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                fullWidth
            />
            <TextField
                id="password"
                label="Senha"
                type="password"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                fullWidth
            />
            <Button
                variant="contained"
                color="primary"
                type="submit"
                fullWidth>
                Cadastrar
            </Button>
        </form>
    )
}

export default DadosUsuario
